{
  "slide": 8,
  "duration": 43.88,
  "text": "The digital platform would not be complete without an NCR management system. So what we do with this NCR management system is to capture your framework of how you deal with non-confirmities, how you rate the severity, how you want them resolved, the timelines, your framework for communication, who is responsible, accountable, consulted, or informed, or whatever you want to do that. But in essence, we are able to give a full audit trail and status levels of every NCR. Where is it sitting? What has been resolved? What is outstanding? What has been put in a parking bay?",
